CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 28, 1956, page A19, reads: "Top winners in Metoka Club's scholarships were Maurice Johnson, first; Robert Russell, Marlene Jones, Joan Graves, Lee Bertha West and Barbara Ashby. They received their awards at the club's annual garden party last Thursday. - 'Teenie' Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Maurice Johnson, Robert Russell, Marlene Jones, Joan Graves, Lee Bertha West, and Barbara Ashby wearing Metoka Club "scholarship" ribbons, posed outdoors in front of tree and Gulf sign
